brief setup (wsl2 nvidia)

first time setup:
follow instructions: https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-downloads?target_os=Linux&target_arch=x86_64&Distribution=WSL-Ubuntu&target_version=2.0&target_type=deb_network
download and
> sudo apt-get install build-essential libopencv-dev cmake
> cmake -B build

build:
> cmake --build build